snippet.title: Minna de Suiri // Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/3023190/_/

Players throw questions at an AI and deduce the correct answers in this competitive multiplayer game. Compete based on your accuracy rate. Have fun with friends while testing your deductive skills and aim to become the ultimate knowledge champion!

Developed by
PushForward
